on: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">大摆裙</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">很受一些单位年会的欢迎，几个年轻女孩认真研究起摆裙的弧度，一个女孩告诉记者：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">我们的演出费用较为宽裕，所以要租一些质量好的衣服，演出效果才好。幸亏这个摆裙剩下的数量还够，不然现在订都不一定能订上了。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">随着电视剧《宫》、《步步惊心》的热映，清代格格装、阿哥装也很火，在年会上表演<font face="Times New Roman">&quot;</font><font face="宋体">穿越</font><font face="Times New Roman">&quot;</font><font face="宋体">会很出彩。不少服装租赁公司向记者反映，与往年最大的不同就是，今年</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">恶搞</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">类的服装非常火爆，</font></span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/nanshi-chenshan/13628.html"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">男</span><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">装</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">天鹅湖装</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、清代皇帝、格格装、小丑装、财神装</font></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的等等。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">提醒：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">由于租来的</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">演出服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经手次数较多，服装除了会沾染污渍外，同时也不排除会传染皮肤病的可能。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/111231/208_111231171637_1.jpg'')" height="426" alt="庆阳礼服" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY5249223P-16203.jpg" width="335" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/111231/208_111231171800_1.jpg'')" height="457" alt="礼服/晚会礼服" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52500N50-214H.jpg" width="294" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,