(47, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: 24pt">文章马伊琍姐弟恋的传奇故事</span></div>\r\n<div align="center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: 16pt">来源：<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/">庆洋制衣</a></span><span style="font-size: 16pt"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/">&nbsp;</a>&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 16pt">时间：</span><span style="font-size: 16pt">2011.12.31</span></div>\r\n<div align="center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><b><span style="font-size: 16pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 15pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt">【</span><span style="font-size: 16pt"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span><font color="#800080">庆洋制衣</font></span></a></span><span style="font-size: 16pt">】</span></strong>文章马伊琍甜蜜婚姻大家都很羡慕，她们的爱情真是一个传奇啊。随着电视剧《奋斗》的开拍，马伊琍和文章再度合作，并都出演其中的主要角色，工作中的频繁接触，终于使得两人的友情升华为爱情。在《奋斗》之后，两人秘密恋爱。</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">文章比马伊琍小了</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">9</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">岁，所以这段</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">姐弟恋</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-size: 15pt">曝光后多少让人觉得有些匪夷所思。让我们看一下这究竟是怎么回事吧！</span></div>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/111231/207_111231173348_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="文章马伊琍姐弟恋的传奇故事" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY525152150-3W09.jpg" width="379" height="498" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">\r\n<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-size: 15pt"><font face="宋体">电视剧《奋斗》中的情节被移植到了现实，<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>向南<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>的婚姻还是<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>轰动了<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>，只不过这次他的对象换成了<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>夏琳<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>。马伊琍、文章，这对相差九岁的姐弟恋，到秘密结婚，两人的闪恋闪婚一直被外界津津乐道。马伊琍与文章上演了真人版<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>奋斗<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;!</span>马伊琍谈求婚过程，没有送花，没有下跪，《奋斗》还在全国热播的时候，<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>夏琳<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>就和<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>向南<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>走到了一起，不得不称赞<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;80</span>后<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>的文章，奋斗的很踏实。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-size: 15pt"><font face="宋体">看他们的穿着就可以看出他们恩爱的甜蜜样子，白色<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><font color="#800080">T<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">恤情侣衫</span></span></font></a></span>，<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US"><font color="#800080">牛仔</font></span></span></a></span>短裤，情侣的最佳装扮。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/111231/207_111231173711_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="文章马伊琍姐弟恋的传奇故事" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52523K50-49552.jpg" width="497" height="377" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">\r\n<div><font face="宋体"><font size="3">　<span style="font-size: 15pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><font size="3">　</font><span style="font-size: 15pt">后来，文章与马伊琍添了一个可爱的小宝宝。随着女儿爱马的诞生，两人有了爱的结晶，工作时也总有个牵挂。两人在繁重的工作之后，回到家还能跟小爱马共享天伦之乐，可以说相当幸福。或许是因为两人并不想将女儿暴露在媒体的闪光灯下，如今两岁的小爱马在家人的保护下茁壮成长，偶尔曝光的照片可以看出绝对是个小萝莉。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</o:p></span></span></font></font></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(48, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center"><b><font size="6"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 22pt">福袋：</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 22pt">购物陶福气</span></font></b></h1>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;【</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">庆洋制衣</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">】</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">淘</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">福袋</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">是日本人在新年最期待的购物活动。</span>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/guanggao-cuxiaofu/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">福袋</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">一般是用各种不透明的纸袋或</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/wufangbudai2/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">购物袋</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">进行包装，其中放入同类的不同商品，进行搭配销售，比如</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">类就会有衣服、</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/wufangbudai2/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">裙子</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">、</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yundong-maoshan/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">帽子</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">等等。福袋涵盖的种类十分丰富，从数码产品、家用电器到服装服饰、日用商品和食物，几乎囊括所有零售商品。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">其实</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">顾客在购买之前并不知道袋子里装了哪些产品，完全是碰运气，这也是福袋受欢迎的原因之一。许多顾客就是为了讨个福气，同时又满足一下自己的好奇心，而购买一些其实并不需要的福袋。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></a></a></a></a></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">福袋</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">其实就是商品打折促销，形式特别、力度较大，比如1万日元的家用电器</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">福袋</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">中可能会有数码照相机和其他小型家电，商品标价远超过1万日元，十分诱人。而在商场内，福袋大致分为3千日元、5千日元、1万日元甚至更高，价格越高的福袋，内含的价值也越高。比如1万日元的</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/nvshi-xifu/13583.html"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">女装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">福袋，包含有1件</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiye-fuzhuang/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">外套</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">、2件-3件</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhengzhuang-chenshan/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">上衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">、1条-2条</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/fushi-xilie/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">裙子</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">还有丝袜等等，组合形式多样。</span></a></a></a></a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(49, 21, '<p>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); letter-spacing: 0pt">【</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,255); letter-spacing: 0pt">庆洋制衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); letter-spacing: 0pt">】</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/pinpaiwenhua/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">原创服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">行业</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">极具潜力，市场发展前景非常广阔，我们相信一定能做好。&rdquo;我们会让设计师</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">原创服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">的概念更好地贯彻到广大消费者的意识中，更加着力于设计师的品牌推广，深入地去探索消费者们的</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/mingxingyewu/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">个性化需求</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">（</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">www.bjqingyang.com</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">）</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">。</span></a></a></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">中国现在的</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/fenzhi/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装市场</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">没有建立起一个良好的、适合设计师成长的环境，没有营造一种健康、向上的设计氛围。在如此尴尬的背景下，仿佛一夜兴起的设计师原创服装概念开始越来越被消费者接受，并掀起追捧热潮。</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h1><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">原创服装设计成为领头羊</span></h1>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">随着互联网的</span><a href="http://zs.efu.com.cn/pengbo/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">蓬勃</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">发展和电子商务的不断攀高，现代人的</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">消费观念已经悄然发生了变化消费者个性化消费需求不断增长，从最初对品牌的盲目崇拜，提升到对产品设计理念的追求；从一直以来稳定发展的品牌经济已经逐步发展到个性化经济。从电子商务行业整体的宏观数据能够看到，近两年来服装部分的整体购物消费水平有所提高。在消费者不断增加的情况下，消费者个性化需求也在随之增长，服装产品越来越趋向于个性化，独具风格的个性品牌成为网络消费的主流。</span></a></div>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&ldquo;随着时尚圈日新月异的发展，每个人都可以成为不可替代的&quot;主角&quot;（</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">www.bjqingyang.com</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">）</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">，将来的时尚潮流将会从穿名牌渐渐转变为穿设计。</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h1><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">原创设计</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">发展</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">形势</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">备受</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">瞩目</span></h1>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">以消费者占主导地位、</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/dingzhiliucheng/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装定制</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">化生产将成为服装业在未来的一个趋势，也是时代发展的</span><a href="http://zs.efu.com.cn/any-all/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">必然</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">结果。因此，</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">原创服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">行业极具潜力，市场发展前景非常广阔，我们相信一定能做好。&rdquo;我们会让设计师</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">原创服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">的概念更好地贯彻到广大消费者的意识中，更加着力于设计师的品牌推广，深入地去探索消费者们的个性化需求。&rdquo;B2C、C2C市场普遍依靠、附着制造业，产出销售的产品都千篇一律，缺乏设计精神、理念，单一的产出已经越来越无法满足消费者们日益增长的个性化、多样化、专业化的要求。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">我们期待</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">2012会有大的改观。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">（</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">www.bjqingyang.com</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">）</span></a></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', '');
