(55, 21, '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">市场现状</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">：</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">参数指标拿不出</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　　</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保暖、防风防水、透气性强等特点，以</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chongfengyi/"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255)">冲锋衣</span></strong></a><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255)"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font color="#000000">为代表的<strong><span style="color: #0000ff">户外运动服装</span></strong>在今冬备受青睐。</font></span></span></p>\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　　款式和<strong><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianliaozhishi/">面料</a></strong>看起来差不多的<strong>冲锋衣</strong>，价格却相差悬殊。比如，在一些大商场的户外用品专柜，知名品牌的含内胆冲锋衣售价高达几千元，最贵的甚至上万元；而在一些商场推出的打折专柜上，有的<strong>冲锋衣</strong>仅售三四百元，看起来跟数千元的也没多大区别；在一些路边小店内，同样标称&quot;冲锋衣&quot;的服装，价格差异也较大。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102101143_1.jpg'')" height="443" alt="冲锋衣" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52A5DZ-1U35.jpg" width="271" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">行业缺乏生产标准，厂家</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">以次充好</span></h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　　现在<strong>户外运动服装</strong>中，以次充好、高价低质现象比比皆是，扰乱了市场正常经营秩序。代理户外用品知名品牌的不少经销商都希望相关部门尽快出台行业规范标准。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">近期，以冲锋衣为代表的<strong>户外运动服装</strong>生产市场的确存在不少问题，目前，全球户外用品中穿着类的中国都能造得出，不少中国总代理商取得代理权后只让品牌公司出版样，自己在国内找生产厂家、在国内采购<strong>冲锋衣面料</strong>，但国内生产的户外服装面料防风、透气性不强，尤其是这几年原材料价格上涨，有的生产厂家为了降低成本，进一些质量比较差的<strong>冲锋衣面料</strong>，标的都是聚酯纤维，外行人从外观上看不出多少差别。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　</span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="width: 294px; cursor: pointer; height: 571px" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102101218_1.jpg'')" height="672" alt="冲锋衣面料" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52B52030-2Y09.jpg" width="349" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chongfengyi/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0)">冲锋衣选择建议</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　　</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 市民在选购冲锋衣时，如果看重带内胆<strong>冲锋衣</strong>的保暖效果，就不要随便到街边小店或者网上随意购买，走时尚路子的户外运动品牌用的面料普遍一般，而走专业渠道的用的则大多是好料。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102101312_1.jpg'')" height="401" alt="户外运动服装" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52C554F-31411.jpg" width="445" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">相关推荐：</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/contact/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装定制厂家</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/pinpaiwenhua/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装品牌</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/join-us-designer/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装设计</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/fuzhuangdapei/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服装搭配</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chongfengyi/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">冲锋衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/huwai-yundong/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">户外运动</span>&nbsp;</a></a></a></a></a></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(56, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="width: 456px; cursor: pointer; height: 448px" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102101821_1.jpg'')" height="750" alt="羽绒服选购标准" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52E5D10-45405.jpg" width="750" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">羽绒服含绒量不是越多越好</span></h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">在某品牌</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yurongfu2/"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255)">羽绒服</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">内侧标牌上有填充物100%聚酯纤维、</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">含绒量</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">80%等相关数据。相关行业专家提醒，购买</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">羽绒服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">，首先要看的就是含绒量与充绒量，因为</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">含绒量</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">的高低与充绒量的多少，直接影响羽绒服的蓬松度和保暖性。一件衣服的含绒量达到70%以上时，才具备羽绒服的保暖性。然后要看羽绒服的面料，如果面料和里料线缝不整，有可能导致毛丝钻出，影响美观和舒适性。最后要注意羽绒服的透气性，可通过羽绒服的回弹性检测，如果</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255)">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">内部空气不易排出，就说明透气性不强。消费者在选购过程中，切莫一味儿贪图便宜，要尽量选择正规固定店铺，并要认真查看羽绒质量，小心商家在制作过程中调包，以次充好，偷工减料。</span></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">在国家对羽绒服各项</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/fanghanfu/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255)">标准</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">作出的规定中，要求含绒量要达到50%&nbsp;，但对充绒量却没有具体数值的要求，而</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">充绒量</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">的多少直接影响到羽绒服的保暖程度，也就是充绒量越高，羽绒服的保暖效果越好。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">含绒量不是越高越好。基本上含绒量保持在</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">70%～80%就是比较合适的，与同等质量的80%～90%的含绒量的羽绒相比，保暖性相差无几。</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="width: 461px; cursor: pointer; height: 486px" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102102020_1.jpg'')" height="750" alt="羽绒服面料" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52F50210-551D.jpg" width="750" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">羽绒服选购窍门</span></h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">消费者在购买羽绒服时不仅要看含绒量，更要看充绒量，这样才能选到保暖效果好的羽绒服。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">羽绒服上的各种标记应当齐全，比如：厂名、厂址、面料的成分含量、羽绒的种类及含绒量、充绒量的指标，洗涤标识、质量等级、执行标准代号等等。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">相关推荐：</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/contact/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装定制厂家</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/pinpaiwenhua/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装品牌</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/join-us-designer/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装设计</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yurongfu2/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianfu2/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">棉服</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chongfengyi/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">冲锋衣</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yundong-fengyi/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: none underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">风衣</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment--></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(57, 21, '<div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">庆洋制衣</span></a></span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">】</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">近日，市民刘先生向本报反映和平路上某商场8楼<strong>羽绒服</strong>节的促销怪现象。昨天，和平区发改委(物价局)接到本报转述的举报后，负责执法工作的发改委副主任赵延庆带领一干执法人员赶赴上述商场。经检查，该商场存在严重价格欺诈行为，责令其立即整改。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">促销广告执行缩水</span></h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">早</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">上</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">在和平路的一侧立着一个数米高的大幅广告牌，在&ldquo;冬季</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yundongfu/"><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">节&rdquo;几个大字之下，&ldquo;单件</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">50多家厂商年终清库存99元起&rdquo;&ldquo;满200元立减180现金&rdquo;的字样十分醒目，下面列举的20多种</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">品牌囊括目前大多数知名品牌。广告中显示的商场门前，三个身穿</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的人，举着印满上述广告语的&ldquo;盒子&rdquo;吸引着路人的眼球。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">价格欺诈</span></h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">赵延庆指出，此商场的羽绒服促销存在严重的价格欺诈行为。首先，违反价格承诺，</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">这样</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">不能把顾客忽悠来了，又改变承诺，这是一种价格欺诈；很多厂家不明确标价，价签使用不规范；虚构原价。法律规定，虚构原价是一种严重的价格欺诈行为，国家对这种行为的处罚是相当严厉的。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　基于上述理由，和平区物价局责令该商场从昨日起立即整改，所有商品明码标价，把虚构原价一律取缔，标注真实价格，整改时间定为三天。1月4日，该商场须向和平区物价局递交整改报告，如不按要求整改，可能面临停业整顿，不排除建议工商局吊销执照的可能。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102165211_1.jpg'')" height="225" alt="羽绒服促销  涉嫌价格欺诈" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52H2KZ-B456.jpg" width="300" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(58, 21, '<p>眼下又是冬季，户外运动发烧友们又开始准备为自己购入一套户外装备了。冲锋衣，绝对的必备之物。对于一个户外发烧友如果没有一套顶级的冲锋衣显然是不合格的。国内外各大品牌冲锋衣相信大多数驴友都比笔者还要清楚，今天就给那些刚入门的驴友们说什么牌子的冲锋衣好？国内外冲锋衣哪个牌子好？不多说，看下面的：</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120811/1_120811090223_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="冲锋衣哪个牌子好？什么牌子的冲锋衣好？" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY52IOP-L009.jpg" width="700" height="751" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>国际大品牌：</p>\r\n<p>1.哥伦比亚冲锋衣，这个品牌就算不是驴友，相信也有不少人都知道吧。Columbia品牌创立于1938年，深得户外活动发烧友拥戴之余，更大受美国、日本、香港等世界各地潮流人士欢迎，更为Columbia奠下户外服装品牌先驱的地位。无论是款式和性能都堪称顶级</p>\r\n<p>2.始祖鸟冲锋衣，著名的加拿大户外品牌，独特的工艺和不断疯狂追求的技术，始祖鸟这个户外品牌现已成为北美乃至全球堪称一绝的顶级户外品牌。不管您信不信，拥有一件您就知道。</p>\r\n<p>3.THE NORTH FACE 乐斯菲斯，中文名译为北面，这个户外品牌是当初美国最全面的户外装备品牌，产品包括外套，滑雪服，背包，帐篷等一系列户外用品。无论哪一个产品都是那样的出色。国际地位丝毫不逊色与前两位。</p>\r\n<p>当然还有很多知名国际品牌，在此就不一一列举，中国的户外品牌又有哪些呢？</p>\r\n<p>1.探路者</p>\r\n<p>2.奥索卡</p>\r\n<p>3.极星</p>\r\n<p>4.龙鸟</p>\r\n<p>5.慕士塔格(Muztaga)</p>\r\n<p>6.雪狼</p>\r\n<p>7.极地</p>\r\n<p>还有其他一些品牌近年来都很活跃，也许是商家看见这户外装备这块市场的潜力巨大，但笔者认为只有品质过硬的户外冲锋衣才会被旅游们喜爱！</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ff0000">与这些大品牌不同的是，庆洋制衣近年来已为不少企业、户外用品店提供专业的冲锋衣批量制作服务，虽然没有大品牌的知名度，但是做工和价格却有着足够的优势！庆洋制衣竭诚欢迎广大企业来采购员工冲锋衣！来电咨询，我们将给您意想不到的实惠和服务！</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ff0000">产品推荐：<a target="_blank" href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chongfengyi/">冲锋衣</a> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianfu2/">棉服</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
