(72, 21, '<p><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size: large"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奥索卡新型保暖防静电材料备受欢迎</span></span></h1>\r\n<!--EndFragment--></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奥索卡是以专业户外产品为主，最近奥索卡采用了一种新型保暖又防静电的材料。奥索卡</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">新雪丽</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3M高效暖绒棉风衣，针对因户外环境中静电对身体环境以及电子器材等造成的不便，选用新雪丽&reg;AS型保温材料。该材料防静电能力出色，被广泛使用在航空航天、精密电子等领域的专业级防静电材料，它继承了3M暖绒的优良保暖效果。克洛值达到4.70，保暖效果远远超越普通纤维。新雪丽&reg;高效暖绒的保暖性，是普通保暖材料的2倍，是羽绒服的1.5倍，被誉为世界上最好的薄型保暖材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120929/1_120929170517_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="奥索卡新型保暖防静电材料备受欢迎" src="/uploads/allimg/c130506/13CS153B3R0-14300.jpg" width="367" height="435" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">当你看到手指接触物体时发出的&ldquo;哒&rdquo;的一声并伴着光亮。这就是静电释放过程</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">静电在人体内堆积，会引起脑神经细胞膜电流传导异常，影响中枢神经，从而导致血液酸碱度和机体氧特性的改变，影响机体的生理平衡，使人出现头晕、头痛、烦躁、失眠、食欲不振、精神恍惚等症状。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120929/1_120929170600_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="奥索卡新型保暖防静电材料备受欢迎" src="/uploads/allimg/c130506/13CS15401H30-23133.jpg" width="550" height="368" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">静电干扰还可改变人体体表的正常电位差，影响心肌正常的电生理过程，同时也会干扰人体血液循环、免疫和神经系统，影响各脏器（特别是心脏）的正常工作，有可能引起心率异常和心脏早搏。在冬季，约三分之一心血管疾病的发生与静电有关。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120929/1_120929170600_2.jpg'')" border="0" alt="奥索卡新型保暖防静电材料备受欢迎" src="/uploads/allimg/c130506/13CS154395540-33516.jpg" width="550" height="368" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奥索卡&reg;新雪丽&reg;高效暖绒棉风衣，外层为防风防水的压胶风衣，内里是新雪丽&reg;高效暖绒棉服，AS型保温材料有效防止静电产生。可以根据不同的天气和环境自由搭配，Zip-In&nbsp;的设计使拆卸过程简单方便，更轻薄的材质也更利于收纳携带。在气候多变的户外旅途，无须更多准备，你就可以让温暖舒适一路随行。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120929/1_120929170600_3.jpg'')" border="0" alt="奥索卡新型保暖防静电材料备受欢迎" src="/uploads/allimg/c130506/13CS155091930-4HG.jpg" width="367" height="433" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">尺码对照表相关文章推荐：</span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&isin;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/chima/31959.html"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">牛仔裤尺码表,庆洋为您解读女士牛仔裤尺码表</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style=