(74, 21, '<p><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; ">际华<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><strong>职业装</strong></a>研究院</span><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; ">作为全国实力的功能性服装和高级定制企业，</span><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; ">近日，<strong>际华职业装研究院</strong>举办2013年一季度新产品推介会，发布最新设计成果。在新产品推介过程中，职业装研究院将防风速干、防化防酸碱、</span><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; ">防辐射</span><span style="text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; ">、防油拒水、防静电、防蚊虫、夜光、阻燃等8个系列的功能性服装产品及其目标客户群进行了详细介绍。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: center; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; "><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiyezhuang/18/" target="_blank"><img src="/uploads/allimg/130409/1_130409174540_1.jpg" width="422" border="0" height="477" alt="职业装" style="cursor:pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/130409/1_130409174540_1.jpg'')" /></a></div>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">际华职业装研究院办好此次2013年一季度新产品推介会，职业装研究院历时4个月，成立功能性服装和高级定制新产品开发小组，深入开展市场调研，了解着装要求和各项技术指标，搜集、比对相关标准，每套设计方案都经过多次论证、修改和集体审议，每件作品都凝聚了设计师的心血。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">积极有效地开发职业装市场，促进职业装板块研发资源共享，是职业装企业面临的重要课题。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">庆洋制衣网预祝</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">际华职业装研究院2013年一季度新产品推介会</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">圆满成功！</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
