(81, 21, '<div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">【<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/">庆洋制衣</a>】据英国媒体日前报道，英国国防部近日向驻阿富汗的士兵们提供了新型</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiye-zhifu/"><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">军装</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，不过这不仅没得到士兵的夸赞，反而遭到抱怨说，这些</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">军服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">不合身且做工粗糙。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">据英国《每日电讯报》12月28日报道，士兵们称这批</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiye-zhifu/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">新</span><span class="15" style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制服</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">非常不合身、设计极差，而且原材料粗糙。据报道，英国国防部为购置这批新新型多地形迷彩</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">共花费了将近4千万英镑。国防部原本打算将这批</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">发放给全部10万名在阿富汗作战的前线士兵，但没想到刚发放了一小部分</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">就引起一片抱怨之声。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; margin-right: 14.25pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(43,43,43); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">来自北爱尔兰38旅的士兵克丽茜&bull;罗杰斯讽刺说：&ldquo;这</span><span style="font-weight: bold