le="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)">和</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)">帽子</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)">后，有的感动得热泪满眶，有的露出开心的笑容。</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(88, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">【</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">庆洋制衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">】</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">近日</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">,</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">在举行的2011(第二届)广州</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/fushi-xilie/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">服饰</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">文化周高峰论坛暨颁奖典礼上，记者对与会的百家</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">企业进行了外贸生存状况的调查。中小</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">企业融资成本困难，优惠扶持政策的宣传渠道较窄，税收、人力成本、电荒、普惠政策落实不力等仍是受访企业普遍面临的问题。从事外贸的企业出现利润下滑</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">,</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">影响企业利润下滑的原因以原材料上涨及人工材料上涨为主，伴随有人民币升值、利润率下滑等原因。</span></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">成本</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">不断增加</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;外贸</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">部分企业</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">临时</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">关门</span></h2>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">广州市</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">制衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">行业商会副会长李声治昨日告诉本报记者说，已经留意到部分做外贸的中小型服装生产企业因订单匮乏而临时关门的现象。番禺南村好几个老板原本是做外贸的，但是他们近期纷纷向其求救，希望在欧美采购量下降、汇率波动明显的背景下，找点时间短的&ldquo;代工单&rdquo;做做，好让企业不至于倒掉。</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">李声治说，国内品牌企业今年最大的压力是成本上涨的。去年原材料、人工成本的上涨导致企业的支出增加</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">而在终端市场只能</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">靠</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">提价解决一半的问题。剩下一半的成本上涨压力得靠劳动生产率的提高和使用机械代替人工来解决。只能解决部分的，就会导致今年服装的利润率下降。解决不了的，企业就会倒下。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">中国纺织工业协会副秘书长夏令敏昨日在电话中告诉记者，受欧美经济不明朗因素影响，导致欧美区域内服装需求增速下降，这个也是我国服装出口增速放缓的主要原因。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">　　出口形势的恶化，将逐步向国内市场传导，首当其冲的是就业市场！今年与2008年的情况有点类似，去年到外向型服装类企业就业难度明显增加。员工薪水的减少，也导致了消费能力降低，导致国内消费疲软。</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(89, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">【<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/">庆洋制衣</a>】近日，由中国服装协会主办、杉杉集团承办的中国服装协会职业装研究中心年会暨杉杉&middot;</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiye-gongzhuang/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">职业装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">功能</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianliaozhishi/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">面料</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">技术交流会在浙江宁波召开。</span></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">2011年，</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">职业装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">研究中心启动了&ldquo;中国职业装技术规范与服务规范&rdquo;制定工作，参加了服装行业&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;发展纲要制定工作</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">；</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">搭建了与政府及公共事业部门的沟通桥梁</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">；</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">参加了非粘合衬西服标准研究工作</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">；</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">调研先进制造与&ldquo;两化&rdquo;的深度融合</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">；</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">推动了职业装人体数据库研究与应用</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">；</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">举办了新材料应用研究与新材料技术交流会。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">2012年职业装研究中心将展开专题调研工作，摸清行业发展现状、工作要点，将具体工作落实到位，把目标、措施理清楚，尽量把职业装功能性标准提早制定出来。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">会上，<strong>职业装</strong>研究中心核心会员企业分别就企业基本情况、产品种类、用工成本、企业在招标过程中遇到的主要问题、对国内职业装市场的看法、需要职业装研究中心提供服务等问题进行了介绍、交流。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">另外，与会领导、专家、企业家代表还就中国服装协会职业装研究中心制定的《职业装服务规范》、《职业服装通用技术规范》、《非粘合衬西服》标准进行了深入探讨与交流。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会后，与会人员参观了杉杉时尚工业园，包括杉杉合作的国际品牌以及先进的</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/zhiye-fuzhuang/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">西服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">生产流水线。大家对杉杉多年来取得的成就表示敬仰，认为非常值得学习，通过参观发现差距，找到了方向。</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(90, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">【</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">庆洋制衣</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">】新的研究结果表明，男士</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/lingdai/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">领带</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">扎得太紧会增加患眼病的危险，这主要是因为</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">领带</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">扎得过紧使眼睛的压力增大，从而导致眼疾的发生。</span></a></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">伦敦</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">一位</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">医师说：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">主要看你的病人是否眼部压力过重，如果他们的</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">领带</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">扎得太紧，那么就有必要检查一下了。&rdquo;青光眼在英、美两国是导致可预防性眼部失明的主要原因，多数都是在眼中流体增多，造成眼部压力过大，损坏眼神经的情况下发生的。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">纽约</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">负责此项研究</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">的一位</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">专家介绍，</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt">领带</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">扎得紧会压迫颈部的静脉血管，导致更多的血液涌到眼部，从而使眼部压力增大。&ldquo;眼部压力过大，最终可能对眼睛造成比青光眼更严重的损害。</span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/lingdai/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline">领带</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">扎得紧和脖子比较粗的男士都应警惕眼神经遭受长期损害。&rdquo;</span></a></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">这项新的研究可以帮助眼科医生在做检查时辨别出是随着年老体弱而导致的长期眼部压力增大还是短暂因素造成的眼部压力过大。据医学专家介绍，体质衰弱是导致青光眼的最主要因素。</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', ''),
(91, 21, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt"><b><span style="font-size: 16pt"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span><font color="#800080">庆洋制衣</font></span></a></span></b><b><span style="font-size: 16pt">：</span></b><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">很多明星都赶在最后时刻送上对新年的祝福和对</span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">2012</span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">年的期盼，而赵薇老公黄有龙也是在微博大晒全家福。其中爱妻赵薇的大眼十分抢镜，但却被&ldquo;长江后浪推前浪&rdquo;的宝贝女儿小四月抢了风头，大大的脑门和大大的眼睛十分可爱，并且渐渐懂事的她还学会了在拍照时吐出舌头卖萌。</span></div>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120106/207_120106191221_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="赵薇老公晒全家福  小四月吐舌头卖萌" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY53491R0-13K7.jpg" width="669" height="447" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 30pt"><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">赵薇的大眼十分抢镜，白色</span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt"><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span><span><font color="#800080">羽<span>绒服</span></font></span></span></a></span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">，毛领的设计很大气，服看起来也很暖和。但却被&ldquo;长江后浪推前浪&rdquo;的宝贝女儿小四月抢了风头，大大的脑门和大大的眼睛十分可爱，并且渐渐懂事的她还学会了在拍照时吐出舌头卖萌。</span></div>\r\n<div style="line-height: 30pt"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120106/207_120106191856_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="赵薇老公晒全家福  小四月吐舌头卖萌" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY534c41Z-21621.jpg" width="380" height="500" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">\r\n<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 30pt"><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">赵薇</span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 15pt">35</span><span style="backgro