(109, 21, '<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012年7月14（周六）</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">庆洋</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10.5pt; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">文化衫</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">厂家，启动</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012年&ldquo;和达杯&rdquo;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">自绘文化衫大赛，每年都有<strong>文化衫设计（<a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/wenhuashan/">http://www.bjqingyang.com/</a>）</strong>赛事，今年是第</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">12赛事。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">此次比赛将会有近</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">150名</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/gongyingxinxi/12151.html"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10.5pt; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">文化衫设计</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">选手参赛，届时，将为大家呈现一场别具风格的</span><span><a hr