(129, 21, '<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">近日，&ldquo;毒校服&rdquo;事件传的沸沸扬扬，学生是祖国的未来和希望，是每一个家庭的心肝，</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">对于</span><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/xiaofu/" target="_blank">校服</a></span></strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">质量问题&ldquo;屡抽屡中&rdquo;的生产厂商，能否设立一个黑名单来提醒学校？质监部门介绍，黑名单虽然还没有，但从质监部门的角度来说，对不合格的校服生产厂家名单会在网上进行公开。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes''; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:''宋体''; ">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes''; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:''宋体''; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes''; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:''宋体''; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">不合格校服生产厂家名单曝光如下：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o: