(146, 3, 0, '衬衫新产品：抗暑热“日光衬衫”', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/hangyexinwen/33274.html', 1367899012, 1, 0, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}衬衫,日光衬衫,衬衫新产品{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}最近，在热传一种能抗暑热的“日光衬衫”，此衬衫是有印度加尔各答GonChaudhury研究，他阐述了一种新的理念“日光衬衫”，该衬衫内置太阳能电池和风扇。{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}衬衫新产品：抗暑热“日光衬衫”{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify; ">最近，在热传一种能抗暑热的&ldquo;日光衬衫&rdquo;，此衬衫是有印度加尔各答GonChaudhury研究，他阐述了一种新的理念&ldquo;日光衬衫&rdquo;，该内置太阳能电池和风扇。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">GonChaudhury先生说，他们正开发一种技术，将一块小太阳能电池镶嵌到衬衫纤维或者其口袋中，印度时报报道。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: 