(180, 3, 0, ' 岁末服装租赁市场火爆(图) ', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/hangyexinwen/15969.html', 1367899045, 1, 0, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}服装，服装租赁，演出服{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}随着元旦、春节临近，各单位企业年会扎堆举行，演出服装租赁行业也忙得不亦乐乎，想要租赁到满意的演出服，建议大家提前15天预约。{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}岁末服装租赁市场火爆(图){/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}<h1 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<h1 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<h1 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 22pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">岁末服装租赁市场火爆<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">图</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 22pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2011年12月3</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">日&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：</span><span style="color: #0000ff"><u><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">雅迪儿制衣</span></u></span><span><span class="15" style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;编辑：00</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;【</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">】</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">随着元旦、春节临近，各单位企业年会扎堆举行，演出服装租赁行业也忙得不亦乐乎，想要租赁到满意的</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，建议大家提前<font face="Times New Roman">15</font><font face="宋体">天预约。</font></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">行业人士透露：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">现在的经营状况出乎我的意料，每天都能借出几十套</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">。</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">主持人服装</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、民族舞、印度舞、现代舞的</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">我们备了很多货，也很受欢迎。</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">服装租赁手追捧</span></h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">各家服装租赁公司的价格也不尽相同，根据服装种类不同，每件每天在<font face="Times New Roman">50</font><font face="宋体">～</font><font face="Times New Roman">200</font><font face="宋体">元上下浮动。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　跳开场舞的</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">很受一些单位年会的欢迎，几个年轻女孩认真研究起摆裙的弧度，一个女孩告诉记者：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">我们的演出费用较为宽裕，所以要租一些质量好的衣服，演出效果才好。幸亏这个摆裙剩下的数量还够，不然现在订都不一定能订上了。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">随着电视剧《宫》、《步步惊心》的热映，清代格格装、阿哥装也很火，在年会上表演<font face="Times New Roman">&quot;</font><font face="宋体">穿越</font><font face="Times New Roman">&quot;</font><font face="宋体">会很出彩。不少服装租赁公司向记者反映，与往年最大的不同就是，今年</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">恶搞</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">类的服装非常火爆，</font></span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">天鹅湖装</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、清代皇帝、格格装、小丑装、财神装</font></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的等等。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">提醒：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">由于租来的</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">演出服装</span><span s