(184, 3, 0, ' 黄奕素颜穿棉服捧场舞台版《天龙八部》 ', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/hangyexinwen/15975.html', 1367899048, 1, 0, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}黄奕棉服，黄奕舞台版《{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}12月15日，香港著名导演钱永强、音乐制作人金培达、著名动作指导元彬共同创作的舞台版《天龙八部》在北京进行了首演，刘璇、林依轮、黄奕等众多圈内艺人前来捧场。此次的首演获{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}黄奕素颜穿棉服捧场舞台版《天龙八部》{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}<div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: center">\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">【</span><span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; backgroun