(235, 3, 0, '老年人存款当心被穿着银行工作服保险推销员忽悠', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/hangyexinwen/16523.html', 1367899134, 1, 1, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}工作服,职业装,老年人存款{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}现在生活越来越富裕了，有更多的人会去银行存款，在银行营业大厅，会有穿着银行工作服的理财人员，再给你讲述理财是，可得多个心眼了。昨日，岳麓工商分局发布今年第一号消费{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}老年人存款当心被穿着银行工作服保险推销员忽悠{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">老年人存款当心</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">被穿着银行工作服保险</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">推销员</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">忽悠</span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">现在生活越来越富裕了，有更多的人会去银行存款，</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">在银行营业大厅，</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">会有穿着银行工作服的理财人员，再给你讲述理财是，</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">可得多个心眼了。昨日，岳麓工商分局发布今年第一号消费警示，提醒市民尤其是老年朋友当心被穿着银行工作服的保险业务员忽悠了。</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">个案：</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&ldquo;<font face="宋体">存款到期</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">才发现是保险</font></span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　在岳麓工商分局发布此次消费警示涉及的案例中，高大爷的遭遇颇具代表性。据高大爷在湖南大学法学院读书的孙子介绍，去年<font face="Times New Roman">3.15</font><font face="宋体">日，爷爷在一国有银行营业大厅准备存钱时，被身穿类似银行工作服的某保险公司业务员王某诱导，王某称可以帮高大爷办理</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">年期存款业务，利息高，期间如果要钱用，可以随时取，等有钱时再补齐就行。见王某穿着很像银行工作人员，高大爷便签了字，将原本想存定期的</font><font face="Times New Roman">5000</font><font face="宋体">元钱买了保险。今年到期取钱时，高大爷才恍然大悟发现自己的存款竟然变成了保险。</font></span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">警示：</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">存定期一定得上银行柜台</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">岳麓工商分局<font face="Times New Roman">12315</font><font face="宋体">、岳麓消委发出今年第一号消费警示：提醒老年人在银行存定期时，首先一定要在银行柜台上办理，对于推销保险的人员要多留个心眼，不要被保险业务员的穿着和花言巧语所迷惑；如果想购买保险，可约时间在有家人在场的情况下，看清楚各项条款后再行签约。另外，如果老人当时糊里糊涂签了约，可以依据中国银监会</font><font face="Times New Roman">2010</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">11</font><font face="宋体">月</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">日发出的关于叫停保险公司在银行网点内</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">驻点销售</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">紧急文件</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">规定，及时取消保险合同。</font></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">来源长沙晚报<font face="Times New Roman">)&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- Baidu Button BEGIN -->\r\n    <div id="bdshare" class="bdshare_b" style="line-height: 12px;"><img src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY53603D10-3X31.jpg" />\r\n		\r\n	</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript" id="bdshare_js" data="type=button&amp;uid=524715" ></script>\r\n<script type="text/javascript" id="bdshell_js"></script>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n	document.getElementById("bdshell_js").src = "http://bdimg.share.baidu.com/static/js/shell_v2.js?cdnversion=" + new Date().getHours();\r\n</script>\r\n<!-- Baidu Button END -->\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><font color="#0000ff">【<span style="color: #0000ff"></span></font><span style="color: #0000ff">】&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【</span><span style="color: #0000ff">】</span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''litpic''}/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY53603D10-3X31_lit.jpg{/dede:field}\r\n'),
(236, 3, 0, '校服诟病：家长不满意质量 学生不爱穿', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/hangyexinwen/16537.html', 1367899135, 1, 0, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}校服,校服厂家,校服定做{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}“家长不满意质量，学生不爱穿”，是目前一些校服饱受诟病的地方。统一穿着校服的最初用意是避免学生在衣着上互相攀比的不良倾向，培养学生集体主义精神和集体荣誉感，也便于{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}校服诟病：家长不满意质量 学生不爱穿{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}<h1 style="text-align: center"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">校服诟病</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">：家长不满意质量</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&nbsp;学生不爱穿</span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">　　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&ldquo;家长不满意质量，学生不爱穿&rdquo;，是目前一些<span style="color: #000000"><strong></strong></span>饱受诟病的地方。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">　　统一穿着校服的最初用意是避免学生在衣着上互相攀比的不良倾向，培养学生集体主义精神和集体荣誉感，也便于社会监督其行为。但现阶段，孩子们对于校服的讨伐之声不绝于耳，很多<span style="color: #000000"><strong></strong></span>在他们看来是&ldquo;样式难看，不分男女，缺乏美感&rdquo;。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">　　针对<strong>校服质量</strong>，家长们近年来的质疑声越来越多。有家长反映，一些学校的校服是100％的化纤<span style="color: #000000"><strong></strong></span>，洗两次后不仅起球，有的地方还脱了线。因为投诉无门，家长们只好根据校服的<strong>款式</strong>和颜色为孩子换<strong>面料</strong>另做一套。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">　　据了解，虽然已经有相关的国家标准，但广州、深圳、珠海等地都根据其地域特点，制定有符合本地实际情况的校服标准。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">　　广州市在2004年就出台了《广州市学生校服质量技术要求指导意见》，对校服的甲醛含量、纤维成分含量、起球、耐洗色牢度等指标制定标准。该《意见》规定，从2004年秋季开始，广州市各中小学校在与校服生产厂家签订的生产合同中，要明确规定校服的具体质量指标，并作为质量验收标准。该《意见》同时规定，学校必须指定专人负责校服的质量管理和验收，加强对校服加工全过程的质量监控，尤其要对原材料和成品质量把关。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">北京</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">雅迪儿制衣厂（QinYa）专业提供<span style="color: #000000"><strong></strong></span>制作,<strong>校服订做</strong>加工,校服生产厂家定制服务。<span style="color: #000000"><strong></strong></span>自产自销，独立庆洋品牌服装，工艺精湛，价格公道！同时为你提供全面的服装定做制作、批发供应、团购、加工厂家等相关信息。咨询电话：400-600-1689</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment--></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- Baidu Button BEGIN -->\r\n    <div id="bdshare" class="bdshare_b" style="line-height: 12px;"><img src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY53603D10-3X31.jpg" />\r\n		\r\n	</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript" id="bdshare_js" data="type=button" ></script>\r\n<script type="text/javascript" id="bdshell_js"></script>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">\r\n	document.getElementById("bdshell_js").src = "http://bdimg.share.baidu.com/static/js/shell_v2.js?cdnversion=" + new Date().getHours();\r\n</script>\r\n<!-- Baidu Button END -->\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0pt 2.25pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="tex